@startuml SD-05_User_Management

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 300

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
    FontStyle plain
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ArrowThickness 1
    ArrowFontColor #000000
    ArrowFontSize 16
    LifeLineBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderThickness 1
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
    GroupBorderColor #888888
    GroupBorderThickness 1
    GroupHeaderFontColor #000000
    DividerBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
    DividerFontColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    ParticipantBorderThickness 1
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #999999
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

actor       "Admin"      as Admin
participant "Web UI"     as UI
participant "Controller" as Ctrl
participant "Service"    as Svc
database    "Database"   as DB

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Invite Member ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Admin -> UI  : Enter email + role
UI   -> Ctrl : POST .../members { email, role }
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc  : addMember(orgId, dto)
activate Svc
Svc  -> DB   : find user by email\n(create stub if not found)
Svc  -> DB   : check duplicate + save member
DB  --> Svc  : savedMember
Svc --> Ctrl : member
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> UI  : 201 Created
deactivate Ctrl
UI  --> Admin : Toast "Invitation sent"

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Update Member Role ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Admin -> UI  : Select new role
UI   -> Ctrl : PATCH .../members/:id { role }
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc  : updateMemberRole(orgId, memberId, dto)
activate Svc
Svc  -> DB   : findOne + save(new role)
DB  --> Svc  : updatedMember
Svc --> Ctrl : member
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> UI  : 200 OK
deactivate Ctrl
UI  --> Admin : Toast "Role updated"

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Remove Member ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Admin -> UI  : Click "Remove"
UI   -> Ctrl : DELETE .../members/:id
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc  : removeMember(orgId, memberId)
activate Svc
Svc  -> DB   : remove(OrganizationMember)
DB  --> Svc  : success
Svc --> Ctrl : { success: true }
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> UI  : 200 OK
deactivate Ctrl
UI  --> Admin : Toast "Member removed"

@enduml
